{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":774,"text":"Right now"},{"time":2515,"text":"you have a movie playing inside your head."},{"time":5989,"text":"It's an amazing multi-track movie."},{"time":8516,"text":"It has 3D vision and surround sound"},{"time":11840,"text":"for what you're seeing and hearing right now,"},{"time":14476,"text":"but that's just the start of it."},{"time":16795,"text":"Your movie has smell and taste and touch."},{"time":21978,"text":"It has a sense of your body,"},{"time":24530,"text":"pain, hunger, orgasms."},{"time":28849,"text":"It has emotions,"},{"time":30890,"text":"anger and happiness."},{"time":34426,"text":"It has memories, like scenes from your childhood"},{"time":38220,"text":"playing before you."},{"time":40920,"text":"And it has this constant voiceover narrative"},{"time":45375,"text":"in your stream of conscious thinking."},{"time":49751,"text":"At the heart of this movie is you"},{"time":54824,"text":"experiencing all this directly."},{"time":59189,"text":"This movie is your stream of consciousness,"},{"time":64881,"text":"the subject of experience"},{"time":66188,"text":"of the mind and the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71326,"text":"Consciousness is one of the fundamental facts"},{"time":73631,"text":"of human existence."},{"time":75648,"text":"Each of us is conscious."},{"time":78580,"text":"We all have our own inner movie,"},{"time":81309,"text":"you and you and you."},{"time":84040,"text":"There's nothing we know about more directly."},{"time":87760,"text":"At least, I know about my consciousness directly."},{"time":91232,"text":"I can't be certain that you guys are conscious."}]},{"cues":[{"time":95230,"text":"Consciousness also is what makes life worth living."},{"time":98658,"text":"If we weren't conscious, nothing in our lives"},{"time":102358,"text":"would have meaning or value."},{"time":105723,"text":"But at the same time, it's the most"},{"time":106889,"text":"mysterious phenomenon in the universe."},{"time":111059,"text":"Why are we conscious?"},{"time":114432,"text":"Why do we have these inner movies?"},{"time":115973,"text":"Why aren't we just robots"},{"time":118226,"text":"who process all this input,"},{"time":120469,"text":"produce all that output,"},{"time":122486,"text":"without experiencing the inner movie at all?"},{"time":126341,"text":"Right now, nobody knows the answers"},{"time":128850,"text":"to those questions."},{"time":130596,"text":"I'm going to suggest that to integrate consciousness"},{"time":134305,"text":"into science, some radical ideas may be needed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139000,"text":"Some people say a science of consciousness"},{"time":141966,"text":"is impossible."},{"time":143918,"text":"Science, by its nature, is objective."},{"time":147686,"text":"Consciousness, by its nature, is subjective."},{"time":151111,"text":"So there can never be a science of consciousness."},{"time":155560,"text":"For much of the 20th century, that view held sway."},{"time":158780,"text":"Psychologists studied behavior objectively,"},{"time":162598,"text":"neuroscientists studied the brain objectively,"},{"time":166660,"text":"and nobody even mentioned consciousness."},{"time":170210,"text":"Even 30 years ago, when TED got started,"},{"time":172966,"text":"there was very little scientific work"},{"time":175348,"text":"on consciousness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177900,"text":"Now, about 20 years ago,"},{"time":179605,"text":"all that began to change."},{"time":182578,"text":"Neuroscientists like Francis Crick"},{"time":185355,"text":"and physicists like Roger Penrose"},{"time":188111,"text":"said now is the time for science"},{"time":190351,"text":"to attack consciousness."},{"time":193127,"text":"And since then, there's been a real explosion,"},{"time":195447,"text":"a flowering of scientific work"},{"time":197784,"text":"on consciousness."},{"time":199048,"text":"And this work has been wonderful. It's been great."},{"time":201087,"text":"But it also has some fundamental"},{"time":203175,"text":"limitations so far."},{"time":207000,"text":"The centerpiece"},{"time":208658,"text":"of the science of consciousness in recent years"},{"time":211478,"text":"has been the search for correlations,"},{"time":213973,"text":"correlations between certain areas of the brain"},{"time":217102,"text":"and certain states of consciousness."},{"time":221120,"text":"We saw some of this kind of work"},{"time":222210,"text":"from Nancy Kanwisher and the wonderful work"},{"time":223970,"text":"she presented just a few minutes ago."},{"time":227246,"text":"Now we understand much better, for example,"},{"time":230809,"text":"the kinds of brain areas that go along with"},{"time":233126,"text":"the conscious experience of seeing faces"},{"time":236497,"text":"or of feeling pain"},{"time":239617,"text":"or of feeling happy."},{"time":242106,"text":"But this is still a science of correlations."},{"time":244922,"text":"It's not a science of explanations."},{"time":248278,"text":"We know that these brain areas"},{"time":250901,"text":"go along with certain kinds of conscious experience,"},{"time":254825,"text":"but we don't know why they do."},{"time":258461,"text":"I like to put this by saying"},{"time":260786,"text":"that this kind of work from neuroscience"},{"time":264183,"text":"is answering some of the questions"},{"time":265929,"text":"we want answered about consciousness,"},{"time":267734,"text":"the questions about what certain brain areas do"},{"time":271507,"text":"and what they correlate with."},{"time":273616,"text":"But in a certain sense, those are the easy problems."},{"time":276772,"text":"No knock on the neuroscientists."},{"time":279213,"text":"There are no truly easy\nproblems with consciousness."},{"time":281834,"text":"But it doesn't address the real mystery"},{"time":286425,"text":"at the core of this subject:"},{"time":288355,"text":"why is it that all that physical processing in a brain"},{"time":292575,"text":"should be accompanied by consciousness at all?"},{"time":295500,"text":"Why is there this inner subjective movie?"},{"time":298706,"text":"Right now, we don't really have a bead on that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301960,"text":"And you might say,"},{"time":303993,"text":"let's just give neuroscience a few years."},{"time":307548,"text":"It'll turn out to be another emergent phenomenon"},{"time":311328,"text":"like traffic jams, like hurricanes,"},{"time":316210,"text":"like life, and we'll figure it out."},{"time":318831,"text":"The classical cases of emergence"},{"time":320902,"text":"are all cases of emergent behavior,"},{"time":324280,"text":"how a traffic jam behaves,"},{"time":326627,"text":"how a hurricane functions,"},{"time":328123,"text":"how a living organism reproduces"},{"time":330316,"text":"and adapts and metabolizes,"},{"time":333905,"text":"all questions about objective functioning."},{"time":336188,"text":"You could apply that to the human brain"},{"time":339010,"text":"in explaining some of the behaviors"},{"time":340519,"text":"and the functions of the human brain"},{"time":342792,"text":"as emergent phenomena:"},{"time":343951,"text":"how we walk, how we talk, how we play chess,"},{"time":348349,"text":"all these questions about behavior."},{"time":350239,"text":"But when it comes to consciousness,"},{"time":352366,"text":"questions about behavior"},{"time":354255,"text":"are among the easy problems."},{"time":357180,"text":"When it comes to the hard problem,"},{"time":358777,"text":"that's the question of why is it"},{"time":361154,"text":"that all this behavior"},{"time":362965,"text":"is accompanied by subjective experience?"},{"time":365810,"text":"And here, the standard paradigm"},{"time":367565,"text":"of emergence,"},{"time":369411,"text":"even the standard paradigms of neuroscience,"},{"time":372358,"text":"don't really, so far, have that much to say."}]},{"cues":[{"time":376801,"text":"Now, I'm a scientific materialist at heart."},{"time":380446,"text":"I want a scientific theory of consciousness"},{"time":384473,"text":"that works,"},{"time":386802,"text":"and for a long time, I banged my head"},{"time":389209,"text":"against the wall"},{"time":390650,"text":"looking for a theory of consciousness"},{"time":392787,"text":"in purely physical terms"},{"time":394543,"text":"that would work."},{"time":395870,"text":"But I eventually came to the conclusion"},{"time":397613,"text":"that that just didn't work for systematic reasons."},{"time":401798,"text":"It's a long story,"},{"time":403733,"text":"but the core idea is just that what you get"},{"time":406450,"text":"from purely reductionist explanations"},{"time":408790,"text":"in physical terms, in brain-based terms,"},{"time":411434,"text":"is stories about the functioning of a system,"},{"time":413549,"text":"its structure, its dynamics,"},{"time":415675,"text":"the behavior it produces,"},{"time":417667,"text":"great for solving the easy problems —"},{"time":419747,"text":"how we behave, how we function —"},{"time":422245,"text":"but when it comes to subjective experience —"},{"time":425698,"text":"why does all this feel like\nsomething from the inside? —"},{"time":429259,"text":"that's something fundamentally new,"},{"time":431334,"text":"and it's always a further question."},{"time":435227,"text":"So I think we're at a kind of impasse here."},{"time":440640,"text":"We've got this wonderful, great chain of explanation,"},{"time":443855,"text":"we're used to it, where physics explains chemistry,"},{"time":447455,"text":"chemistry explains biology,"},{"time":450695,"text":"biology explains parts of psychology."},{"time":454542,"text":"But consciousness"},{"time":456000,"text":"doesn't seem to fit into this picture."},{"time":458771,"text":"On the one hand, it's a datum"},{"time":460661,"text":"that we're conscious."},{"time":462630,"text":"On the other hand, we don't know how"},{"time":463916,"text":"to accommodate it into our\nscientific view of the world."},{"time":467894,"text":"So I think consciousness right now"},{"time":469841,"text":"is a kind of anomaly,"},{"time":472304,"text":"one that we need to integrate"},{"time":474340,"text":"into our view of the world, but we don't yet see how."},{"time":478240,"text":"Faced with an anomaly like this,"},{"time":480168,"text":"radical ideas may be needed,"},{"time":483407,"text":"and I think that we may need one or two ideas"},{"time":486412,"text":"that initially seem crazy"},{"time":488852,"text":"before we can come to grips with consciousness"},{"time":491788,"text":"scientifically."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493880,"text":"Now, there are a few candidates"},{"time":495479,"text":"for what those crazy ideas might be."},{"time":497975,"text":"My friend Dan Dennett, who's here today, has one."},{"time":502317,"text":"His crazy idea is that there is no hard problem"},{"time":504714,"text":"of consciousness."},{"time":506457,"text":"The whole idea of the inner subjective movie"},{"time":509820,"text":"involves a kind of illusion or confusion."},{"time":514432,"text":"Actually, all we've got to do is explain"},{"time":516330,"text":"the objective functions, the behaviors of the brain,"},{"time":519337,"text":"and then we've explained everything"},{"time":521362,"text":"that needs to be explained."},{"time":523837,"text":"Well I say, more power to him."},{"time":526446,"text":"That's the kind of radical idea"},{"time":528460,"text":"that we need to explore"},{"time":530384,"text":"if you want to have a purely reductionist"},{"time":532723,"text":"brain-based theory of consciousness."},{"time":536273,"text":"At the same time, for me and for many other people,"},{"time":538344,"text":"that view is a bit too close to simply"},{"time":540171,"text":"denying the datum of consciousness"},{"time":542192,"text":"to be satisfactory."},{"time":543695,"text":"So I go in a different direction."},{"time":546763,"text":"In the time remaining,"},{"time":547949,"text":"I want to explore two crazy ideas"},{"time":550948,"text":"that I think may have some promise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":554665,"text":"The first crazy idea"},{"time":556285,"text":"is that consciousness is fundamental."},{"time":560910,"text":"Physicists sometimes take\nsome aspects of the universe"},{"time":563751,"text":"as fundamental building blocks:"},{"time":565911,"text":"space and time and mass."},{"time":569660,"text":"They postulate fundamental laws governing them,"},{"time":573270,"text":"like the laws of gravity or of quantum mechanics."},{"time":577160,"text":"These fundamental properties and laws"},{"time":579470,"text":"aren't explained in terms of anything more basic."},{"time":582687,"text":"Rather, they're taken as primitive,"},{"time":585427,"text":"and you build up the world from there."},{"time":588806,"text":"Now sometimes, the list of fundamentals expands."},{"time":593905,"text":"In the 19th century, Maxwell figured out"},{"time":596362,"text":"that you can't explain electromagnetic phenomena"},{"time":599530,"text":"in terms of the existing fundamentals —"},{"time":601881,"text":"space, time, mass, Newton's laws —"},{"time":604950,"text":"so he postulated fundamental laws"},{"time":607521,"text":"of electromagnetism"},{"time":609335,"text":"and postulated electric charge"},{"time":611746,"text":"as a fundamental element"},{"time":613514,"text":"that those laws govern."},{"time":616473,"text":"I think that's the situation we're in"},{"time":619756,"text":"with consciousness."},{"time":621366,"text":"If you can't explain consciousness"},{"time":623851,"text":"in terms of the existing fundamentals —"},{"time":626269,"text":"space, time, mass, charge —"},{"time":628940,"text":"then as a matter of logic,\nyou need to expand the list."},{"time":632370,"text":"The natural thing to do is to postulate"},{"time":634846,"text":"consciousness itself as something fundamental,"},{"time":638102,"text":"a fundamental building block of nature."},{"time":641134,"text":"This doesn't mean you suddenly\ncan't do science with it."},{"time":644102,"text":"This opens up the way for you to do science with it."},{"time":647700,"text":"What we then need is to study"},{"time":649604,"text":"the fundamental laws governing consciousness,"},{"time":652557,"text":"the laws that connect consciousness"},{"time":654937,"text":"to other fundamentals: space, time, mass,"},{"time":657738,"text":"physical processes."},{"time":660674,"text":"Physicists sometimes say"},{"time":662856,"text":"that we want fundamental laws so simple"},{"time":665736,"text":"that we could write them on the front of a t-shirt."},{"time":669538,"text":"Well I think something like that is the situation"},{"time":671259,"text":"we're in with consciousness."},{"time":673127,"text":"We want to find fundamental laws so simple"},{"time":675877,"text":"we could write them on the front of a t-shirt."},{"time":677964,"text":"We don't know what those laws are yet,"},{"time":679539,"text":"but that's what we're after."}]},{"cues":[{"time":683566,"text":"The second crazy idea"},{"time":685983,"text":"is that consciousness might be universal."},{"time":689461,"text":"Every system might have some degree"},{"time":692522,"text":"of consciousness."},{"time":696247,"text":"This view is sometimes called panpsychism:"},{"time":699208,"text":"pan for all, psych for mind,"},{"time":702210,"text":"every system is conscious,"},{"time":703981,"text":"not just humans, dogs, mice, flies,"},{"time":708228,"text":"but even Rob Knight's microbes,"},{"time":710805,"text":"elementary particles."},{"time":712992,"text":"Even a photon has some degree of consciousness."},{"time":715705,"text":"The idea is not that photons are intelligent"},{"time":719484,"text":"or thinking."},{"time":720561,"text":"It's not that a photon"},{"time":721991,"text":"is wracked with angst"},{"time":723436,"text":"because it's thinking, \"Aww, I'm always\nbuzzing around near the speed of light."},{"time":726728,"text":"I never get to slow down and smell the roses.\""},{"time":729720,"text":"No, not like that."},{"time":731864,"text":"But the thought is maybe photons might have"},{"time":734912,"text":"some element of raw, subjective feeling,"},{"time":737535,"text":"some primitive precursor to consciousness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":741687,"text":"This may sound a bit kooky to you."},{"time":744541,"text":"I mean, why would anyone think such a crazy thing?"},{"time":747324,"text":"Some motivation comes from the first crazy idea,"},{"time":750884,"text":"that consciousness is fundamental."},{"time":753030,"text":"If it's fundamental, like space and time and mass,"},{"time":757405,"text":"it's natural to suppose that it might be universal too,"},{"time":760070,"text":"the way they are."},{"time":761970,"text":"It's also worth noting that although the idea"},{"time":763919,"text":"seems counterintuitive to us,"},{"time":765943,"text":"it's much less counterintuitive to people"},{"time":768687,"text":"from different cultures,"},{"time":770418,"text":"where the human mind is seen as much more"},{"time":771938,"text":"continuous with nature."}]},{"cues":[{"time":775010,"text":"A deeper motivation comes from the idea that"},{"time":778744,"text":"perhaps the most simple and powerful way"},{"time":780753,"text":"to find fundamental laws connecting consciousness"},{"time":782987,"text":"to physical processing"},{"time":784967,"text":"is to link consciousness to information."},{"time":788062,"text":"Wherever there's information processing,"},{"time":790073,"text":"there's consciousness."},{"time":791138,"text":"Complex information processing, like in a human,"},{"time":793688,"text":"complex consciousness."},{"time":795220,"text":"Simple information processing,"},{"time":797349,"text":"simple consciousness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":799307,"text":"A really exciting thing is in recent years"},{"time":801638,"text":"a neuroscientist, Giulio Tononi,"},{"time":804903,"text":"has taken this kind of theory"},{"time":806146,"text":"and developed it rigorously"},{"time":808221,"text":"with a mathematical theory."},{"time":810070,"text":"He has a mathematical measure"},{"time":811587,"text":"of information integration"},{"time":813317,"text":"which he calls phi,"},{"time":815236,"text":"measuring the amount of information"},{"time":816843,"text":"integrated in a system."},{"time":818463,"text":"And he supposes that phi goes along"},{"time":820832,"text":"with consciousness."},{"time":822270,"text":"So in a human brain,"},{"time":823591,"text":"incredibly large amount of information integration,"},{"time":826110,"text":"high degree of phi,"},{"time":828144,"text":"a whole lot of consciousness."},{"time":829693,"text":"In a mouse, medium degree\nof information integration,"},{"time":833386,"text":"still pretty significant,"},{"time":834405,"text":"pretty serious amount of consciousness."},{"time":836430,"text":"But as you go down to worms,"},{"time":838695,"text":"microbes, particles,"},{"time":842172,"text":"the amount of phi falls off."},{"time":843706,"text":"The amount of information integration falls off,"},{"time":846139,"text":"but it's still non-zero."},{"time":847587,"text":"On Tononi's theory,"},{"time":849526,"text":"there's still going to be a non-zero degree"},{"time":851733,"text":"of consciousness."},{"time":853562,"text":"In effect, he's proposing a fundamental law"},{"time":856101,"text":"of consciousness: high phi, high consciousness."},{"time":859485,"text":"Now, I don't know if this theory is right,"},{"time":862107,"text":"but it's actually perhaps the leading theory right now"},{"time":865318,"text":"in the science of consciousness,"},{"time":866704,"text":"and it's been used to integrate a whole range"},{"time":868935,"text":"of scientific data,"},{"time":871322,"text":"and it does have a nice property\nthat it is in fact simple enough"},{"time":873565,"text":"you can write it on the front of a t-shirt."}]},{"cues":[{"time":877060,"text":"Another final motivation is that"},{"time":879685,"text":"panpsychism might help us to integrate"},{"time":881736,"text":"consciousness into the physical world."},{"time":884950,"text":"Physicists and philosophers have often observed"},{"time":888127,"text":"that physics is curiously abstract."},{"time":890568,"text":"It describes the structure of reality"},{"time":892716,"text":"using a bunch of equations,"},{"time":894800,"text":"but it doesn't tell us about the reality"},{"time":897824,"text":"that underlies it."},{"time":899392,"text":"As Stephen Hawking puts it,"},{"time":901289,"text":"what puts the fire into the equations?"},{"time":905343,"text":"Well, on the panpsychist view,"},{"time":907961,"text":"you can leave the equations of physics as they are,"},{"time":910600,"text":"but you can take them to be describing"},{"time":912164,"text":"the flux of consciousness."},{"time":913838,"text":"That's what physics really is ultimately doing,"},{"time":915876,"text":"describing the flux of consciousness."},{"time":918205,"text":"On this view, it's consciousness"},{"time":919858,"text":"that puts the fire into the equations."},{"time":924104,"text":"On that view, consciousness doesn't dangle"},{"time":925764,"text":"outside the physical world"},{"time":927440,"text":"as some kind of extra."},{"time":928858,"text":"It's there right at its heart."}]},{"cues":[{"time":932314,"text":"This view, I think, the panpsychist view,"},{"time":935188,"text":"has the potential to transfigure our relationship"},{"time":938489,"text":"to nature,"},{"time":939984,"text":"and it may have some pretty serious social"},{"time":942219,"text":"and ethical consequences."},{"time":945912,"text":"Some of these may be counterintuitive."},{"time":948071,"text":"I used to think I shouldn't eat anything"},{"time":951142,"text":"which is conscious,"},{"time":953604,"text":"so therefore I should be vegetarian."},{"time":956208,"text":"Now, if you're a panpsychist and you take that view,"},{"time":958775,"text":"you're going to go very hungry."},{"time":961505,"text":"So I think when you think about it,"},{"time":962793,"text":"this tends to transfigure your views,"},{"time":964960,"text":"whereas what matters for ethical purposes"},{"time":967203,"text":"and moral considerations,"},{"time":968477,"text":"not so much the fact of consciousness,"},{"time":971554,"text":"but the degree and the complexity of consciousness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":975510,"text":"It's also natural to ask about consciousness"},{"time":977448,"text":"in other systems, like computers."},{"time":980498,"text":"What about the artificially intelligent system"},{"time":982287,"text":"in the movie \"Her,\" Samantha?"},{"time":985729,"text":"Is she conscious?"},{"time":987129,"text":"Well, if you take the informational,"},{"time":988560,"text":"panpsychist view,"},{"time":989740,"text":"she certainly has complicated information processing"},{"time":993211,"text":"and integration,"},{"time":994632,"text":"so the answer is very likely yes, she is conscious."},{"time":997299,"text":"If that's right, it raises pretty serious"},{"time":1000237,"text":"ethical issues about both the ethics"},{"time":1002602,"text":"of developing intelligent computer systems"},{"time":1006123,"text":"and the ethics of turning them off."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1008859,"text":"Finally, you might ask about the consciousness"},{"time":1011359,"text":"of whole groups,"},{"time":1013241,"text":"the planet."},{"time":1015078,"text":"Does Canada have its own consciousness?"},{"time":1018001,"text":"Or at a more local level,"},{"time":1020100,"text":"does an integrated group"},{"time":1021308,"text":"like the audience at a TED conference,"},{"time":1023571,"text":"are we right now having a\ncollective TED consciousness,"},{"time":1027020,"text":"an inner movie"},{"time":1028513,"text":"for this collective TED group"},{"time":1031319,"text":"which is distinct from the inner movies"},{"time":1032999,"text":"of each of our parts?"},{"time":1034088,"text":"I don't know the answer to that question,"},{"time":1036253,"text":"but I think it's at least one"},{"time":1037624,"text":"worth taking seriously."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1040098,"text":"Okay, so this panpsychist vision,"},{"time":1042435,"text":"it is a radical one,"},{"time":1044248,"text":"and I don't know that it's correct."},{"time":1046462,"text":"I'm actually more confident about"},{"time":1048315,"text":"the first crazy idea,"},{"time":1049948,"text":"that consciousness is fundamental,"},{"time":1052117,"text":"than about the second one,"},{"time":1053920,"text":"that it's universal."},{"time":1056141,"text":"I mean, the view raises any number of questions,"},{"time":1058219,"text":"has any number of challenges,"},{"time":1059760,"text":"like how do those little bits"},{"time":1061120,"text":"of consciousness add up"},{"time":1062860,"text":"to the kind of complex consciousness"},{"time":1065157,"text":"we know and love."},{"time":1067480,"text":"If we can answer those questions,"},{"time":1068940,"text":"then I think we're going to be well on our way"},{"time":1070445,"text":"to a serious theory of consciousness."},{"time":1073532,"text":"If not, well, this is the hardest problem perhaps"},{"time":1076920,"text":"in science and philosophy."},{"time":1078764,"text":"We can't expect to solve it overnight."},{"time":1082209,"text":"But I do think we're going to figure it out eventually."},{"time":1085749,"text":"Understanding consciousness is a real key, I think,"},{"time":1088736,"text":"both to understanding the universe"},{"time":1091188,"text":"and to understanding ourselves."},{"time":1093718,"text":"It may just take the right crazy idea."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1096621,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1098612,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}